{"tid":1912243,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔係要建制派贏，但我要白頭佬輸","createTime":"2020-03-06T02:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T05:46:17.000Z","uid":323538,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"44ab38d3c7f3ebe131a17aad92300ed6b626e135","tid":1912243,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n停止與白頭佬合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有議員，團體，苦主<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好比機會佢曝光</span></strong>！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時至今日，大家唔難喺記者招待會、遊行度，仲見到白頭佬攝到位入鏡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因為屌佢老母仲有好撚多人搵佢去囉！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n議員開記招，無咗白頭會收皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n團體搵合作，無咗街工會搞唔成？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n苦主要求助，無第個議員幫到你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個仲搵白頭佬？<br />\n仲送佢曝光、比佢繼續刷存在<br />\n就係送佢去<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">選</span></span></strong>！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係阻撚住地球轉!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>同我一傳十 十傳百</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳開佢!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr